title: Project AM2R - Another Metroid 2 Remake
description:
A wonderful work on the original Metroid II make by DoctorM64! That's what Nintendo needs to do with a beloved IP. Not that joke called Federation Force!
I took the liberty of share the joy. I hope anyone else who was luck to get this piece of art do the same. All Metroid fans have to play this!

Oficial Site:


PS: Nintendo, if you read this and there is any brains left on this company, be smart, hire this guy and help him to make an even better Metroid II. And release this as an oficial remake for God's sake!
